<document>
  <properties>
    <title>Document card</title>
  </properties>

  <body>
   <section name="Document card">
      <span class="shortdesc">What and where are document cards?</span>

    <div class='group'>
     <div class='screenshot'>
      <img src="../../../../images/screenshots/cms_M9/contribs/document_card.png" 
       alt='document cards'/>
     </div>
     <p>
      Document cards. 
      <span class='add'>more about cards in the image</span>
     </p>   
    </div>

    <p>
     You can select a document in the 
     <a href='content_tabulation_panel.html'>content tabulation panel</a> 
     to <a href='./edit_mode.html'>change</a> or
     <a href='./review_mode.html'>review</a> it. The document
     then appears on a <i>document card</i> in the 
     <a href='documents_panel.html'>documents panel</a>. 
     Several documents card can be open on the documents panel at any time.
     They will not all be visible, but lay on top of each other. Only a small
     tab on the upper edge of each card will be visible. 
     You can click on a tab to put another document card on top, so that you
     can see it. 
    </p>

   </section>
  </body>
